Login to Salesforce with an authorized user who has permission to schedule Apex classes.

Go to Setup > Apex Classes.

Click on the "Schedule Apex" button.

Fill in the following details:

Job Name: NightlyBatchJob (or appropriate name)

Apex Class: YourBatchClassName (replace with your batch class)

Frequency: Weekly

Select all days if it should run daily.

Preferred Start Time: 10:00 PM

Click Save.

Verify the job has been scheduled:

Go to Setup > Scheduled Jobs

Confirm that the batch job appears with the correct start time and frequency.
